<p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">2024年2月10日上午，江西软件职业技术大学理事长陈方平、校党委书记、督导专员江延湖、执行校长范红铭在党政办等相关部门负责同志的陪同下，迎着寒风，到学校门口、教学楼看望和慰问在春节期间仍然坚守在工作一线的平安建设处及后勤保障部门的教职员工。</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">学校领导热情地与值班人员一一握手，代表学校送上关怀和温暖，仔细询问节日期间的工作安排等情况，并表示诚挚的敬意，祝在春节假期坚守岗位、辛勤工作的干部职工春节愉快、阖家幸福！</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-10%2011%3A59%3A57%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.jpg?Expires=2022897598&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=WBIZVdHS9kZAewH6NfXEM8AeWp8%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-10%2012%3A00%3A31%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.jpg?Expires=2022897632&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=VUREa6UsDH3PQD5PUu9OvnaMW9A%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-10%2012%3A00%3A43%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.jpg?Expires=2022897644&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=9lhuFP9tlzF%2FZ6XEvgJzUCU9Cpc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">职工们对新春佳节不能和家人团聚都表示理解，感谢学校领导的关心关爱，纷纷表示一定会在节日期间立足本职，坚守岗位，全力做好本职工作，做好春节期间师生安全防范的工作，履职尽责为师生健康保驾护航!</span></p><p style="text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">值此新春佳节之际，学校领导也代表江西软件职业技术大学，向广大师生致以节日的问候，祝愿大家新春快乐，龙行龘龘，前程朤朤，生活䲜䲜！</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p>